===Etymology===
Via {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term/t|ang|sc=unicode|tōdæge}}, {{term||tō dæge||on [the] day|lang=ang}}, made from {{term||tō||at, on|lang=ang}} + {{term||dæge|lang=ang}}, the dative of {{term|dæg|sc=unicode|lang=ang||day}}. See {{term|to|lang=en}} and {{term|day|lang=en}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/təˈdeɪ/}}
* {{audio|en-us-today.ogg|Audio (US)}}
* {{audio|En-uk-today.ogg|Audio (UK)}}
