===Adverb===
{{en-adv|-}}

# On the current [[day]] or [[date]].
#: {{usex|I want this done '''today'''.|lang=en}}
#: {{usex|'''Today''', my brother went to the shops.|lang=en}}
# In the current [[era]]; [[nowadays]].
